        {
            "description": "Set the local send rate divisor for an object. A value of `1` means the object sends every tick (highest rate). A value of `16` means it sends every 16th tick (lowest rate). This is a client-side optimization -- the object still exists on all clients but consumes less bandwidth when you are not the active authority.\n",
            "examples": "",
            "name": "fusion.set_local_send_rate",
            "parameters": [
